| Stat Arb     | Pairs trading, cointegration, PCA                     |
| ML/AI Quant  | NLP, random forests, deep learning                    |
| Crypto Quant | On-chain analysis, arbitrage, altcoins                |
| HFT          | Latency arbitrage, co-location, order book prediction |

